@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@scenarioVersion = {{$timestamp}}

### Cadastro do usuario 1 (dono das categorias) -> 201 sem corpo
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria da Silva",
  "email": "maria.categorias.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login do usuario 1 -> 200 com token
# @name loginUser1
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria.categorias.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Cadastro do usuario 2 (usado para validar isolamento) -> 201 sem corpo
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Joao Pereira",
  "email": "joao.categorias.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Login do usuario 2 -> 200 com token
# @name loginUser2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao.categorias.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Strong@123"
}

### Seed de categorias padrao do usuario 1 (primeira chamada) -> 200 com created: 7
# @name seedFirstCall
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories/seed-defaults
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Seed de categorias padrao do usuario 1 (segunda chamada) -> 200 com created: 0 (idempotente)
# @name seedSecondCall
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories/seed-defaults
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Criacao de categoria com dados validos (usuario 1) -> 201 com a categoria criada
# @name createCategory
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Assinaturas",
  "type": "expense",
  "color": "#3B82F6",
  "icon": "credit-card"
}

### Criacao de categoria com name vazio -> 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "",
  "type": "expense",
  "color": "#3B82F6"
}

### Criacao de categoria com type fora do enum -> 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Categoria invalida",
  "type": "outro",
  "color": "#3B82F6"
}

### Criacao de categoria com color fora do padrao hex -> 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Categoria invalida",
  "type": "expense",
  "color": "azul"
}

### Listagem de categorias do usuario 1 -> 200 com as 7 padrao + a customizada (8 no total)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Listagem de categorias do usuario 2 -> 200 lista vazia (isolamento, seed nao foi chamado para ele)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

### Busca por id da categoria do usuario 1 -> 200 com a categoria
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{createCategory.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Busca por id de categoria inexistente -> 404 category.not.found
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Busca da categoria do usuario 1 usando o token do usuario 2 -> 404 category.not.found (isolamento)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{createCategory.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

### Atualizacao da categoria do usuario 1 -> 200 com a categoria atualizada
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{createCategory.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Assinaturas digitais",
  "color": "#8B5CF6"
}

### Atualizacao com dados invalidos (color fora do padrao hex) -> 422
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{createCategory.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

{
  "color": "invalida"
}

### Atualizacao da categoria do usuario 1 usando o token do usuario 2 -> 404 category.not.found (isolamento)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{createCategory.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Tentativa de invasao"
}

### Exclusao de categoria inexistente -> 404 category.not.found
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}

### Exclusao da categoria do usuario 1 usando o token do usuario 2 -> 404 category.not.found (isolamento)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{createCategory.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser2.response.body.token}}

### Exclusao da categoria do usuario 1 -> 204 sem corpo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{createCategory.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginUser1.response.body.token}}
